{"tid":1033034,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（史健仁）　70年代　香港同中國最有區隔　香港人最有笑容時代","createTime":"2019-02-22T21:03:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-23T00:57:13.000Z","uid":47714,"like":6,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"9708baede16eb56895703f0334ba2bf09884e868","tid":1033034,"uid":47714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T21:03:17.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/julian.yip/posts/10156976929069929\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fjulian.yip%2Fposts%2F10156976929069929&d=gMg1FBwAZA1XbJy1Uvmn1G5ZeM81ILqxQ%2BPX7M1Kayg%3D&h=1d8a1451\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/julian.yip/posts/10156976929069929</a><br />\n<br />\n作者：史健仁<br />\n<br />\n【科技比以前發達，但生活卻比以前壓抑】<br />\n<br />\n想當年，中國同香港仲有區隔，中共嘅黨國資本主義思想仲未殺入香港，「中國經濟發展機遇」仲未係呢個世界出現。個陣英國佬管治香港相當簡單，只要香港人唔製造麻煩比佢哋，佢哋就唔會理香港人。佢哋冇迫香港人唱英國國歌，冇迫香港細路仔愛英女皇及對英國國旗喊，亦冇取消廣東話及正體字。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://is.gd/16pwn4\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fis.gd%2F16pwn4&h=34c6bd01&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7a61f57c83b98b0f04f372d73fba3d6fc706b7b8","tid":1033034,"uid":103156,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T21:29:22.000Z","msg":"窮得快樂，可能你未夠窮"},{"pid":"eb21d3266f17c77d02ce6946268cb72303f9a80a","tid":1033034,"uid":2267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T23:38:38.000Z","msg":"佢哋笑，係因為終於落到嚟香港，逃離中共"},{"pid":"ccebf7db13b55c974a000ffe8f8ba0da53d68132","tid":1033034,"uid":13592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-23T00:04:40.000Z","msg":"有前景 易搵工 肯消費"},{"pid":"425e698c266d7bf66fc53c16febd0219b3e78744","tid":1033034,"uid":33028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-23T00:57:13.000Z","msg":"有抵壘政策喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}